  "time_ut": 1661942049,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is a risk of flooding in several areas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Irrigation Department says that there is a risk of flooding in many low-lying areas of Ratnapura district as the downstream areas of the Kalu Ganga basin have received high rainfall.",
        "Director of Irrigation (Hydrology and Disaster Management) Engineer S.P. said that there may be a risk of flood today (31) or tomorrow (1) in the lowlands belonging to the Kalu Ganga plain in the divisional secretaries of Pelmadulla, Nivitigala, Ratnapura, Kuruvita, Ayagama and Alapatha in that district. Mr. C. Sugeeshwara said.",
        "The District Disaster Management Center says that the heavy rain in Kalutara district is flooding the main road and side roads.",
        "Ms. Sarangi Dhiraratne, Palindanuwara Divisional Secretary, said that many roads have been submerged due to the overflowing of the Maguru River."
      ],
